data.description: Motivated Seller! Offering 3% toward buyers closing cost with full price offer. Welcome to your dream coastal retreat near St. Augustine Beach! This immaculate condo offers a perfect blend of modern elegance and tranquil surroundings. With vaulted ceilings and an abundance of natural light, this home creates a spacious and airy ambiance that will instantly captivate you. Step inside to discover a thoughtfully designed open floor plan that seamlessly integrates the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The primary bedroom is a peaceful oasis, complete with an en-suite bathroom featuring a large shower, and a double vanity. One of the true highlights is the expansive balcony that overlooks the pristine golf course and tranquil pond. Additional features include storage space, washer & dryer, and access to the two community swimming pools. Enjoy the best St. Augustine Beach has to offer from its pristine sandy beaches, charming shops, dining options, and a myriad of outdoor activities. Whether you're a golf enthusiast, nature lover, or simply seeking a tranquil escape, this condo offers it all. Treat yourself to the coastal living experience you've always dreamed of!
